Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.36,0:26:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I discovered that within my soul. Take\Nthat.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.27,0:26:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful. So you can love your cuckoo\Nside. Huh?
