Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.00,0:32:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,develop this because the 400s are far\Nmore powerful than all this. You can be
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.32,0:32:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,mad as all hell and nothing really\Nhappens in the world. But you get up to
