Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.71,1:18:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You got 10 years in solitary.\NThere you got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.84,1:18:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh monastery for one.\NI told you when I lived in a monastery
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.00,1:18:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,for one. Yeah. And the body disappeared.\NI walked into a wall and I walked past a
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.08,1:18:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,mirror. There was somebody in the house.\NI walked past the mirror. There's
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.76,1:18:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody in the house for Christ sake.\NWho is that? Oh my god. It's myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.40,1:18:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprise.\NAll right. So, the the validity of
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.92,1:18:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,calibration of kinesiology. We'll answer\Nquestions about kinesiology. I'm not a
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.71,1:18:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,kinesiologist\Nand people want uh all kinds of detailed
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.52,1:19:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,questions about kinesiology are better\Nto uh you know correspond. There's a
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.64,1:19:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,kinesiology\Nwebsite full of all kinds of experts
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.04,1:19:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,with all kinds of references. If you\Ncan't do it yourself, find somebody that
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.36,1:19:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,can. There's people around that are\Ninterested in this kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.04,1:19:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of uh holistic\Npractitioners that are very good at it,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.04,1:19:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,teach you how. So, I'm not an expert in\Nkinesiology and I explain it. Galileo
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.15,1:19:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,was not an expert in making telescopes.\NYou know, you got a telescope maker. You
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.48,1:19:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,got this telescope. Everybody's looking\Neverybody's backyard with telescopes and
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.32,1:19:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,he went up this way and that's sort of\Nwhere I'm at. I'm not into making
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.04,1:19:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,telescopes and I get all kinds of\Ntechnical questions about kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.23,1:19:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,which I really am not able to answer.\NWe have found that um it's a technique
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.48,1:19:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,available to people who themselves are\Nintegrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.88,1:19:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Integrity means calibrated 200 or over.\NUm there's an enormous amount of power
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.44,1:20:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,given to you. To be able to use\Nkinesiology to find out things is an
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.08,1:20:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,enormous jump in power and that power is\Njust not given to people who would
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.32,1:20:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,misuse it. So, one reason that I delayed\Npublishing Power Versus Force is I
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.64,1:20:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,worried about that. I thought, you know,\NI was going to be using it to invent
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.32,1:20:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,better atomic bombs and kill each other\Nbetter. You know, I can picture Ben Len
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.71,1:20:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,testing kinesiology. Should we hit the\NWorld Trade Center? Yeah. Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.80,1:20:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh\Nso I worried about it and uh anyway it
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.12,1:20:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,later came to me\Nthat it can only be used by integrous
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.36,1:20:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,people for integrous ends. So the\Nintention of the question itself has to
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.52,1:20:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,be integrous\Nand um you can change a non integorous
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.48,1:20:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,question into an integrous one if you\Nrecontextualize it from a different uh
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.08,1:21:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,context. And um the classic one is say\Nin the interest of the good of all of
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.32,1:21:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,life\Nyou know in the interest of the good and
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.60,1:21:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the goodness of all of life for everyone\Nuh I have permission to ask this
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.92,1:21:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,question. So then you ask I have\Npermission to ask this question and even
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.04,1:21:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,though we've done it hundreds hundreds\Nof thousands of times as you've seen
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.23,1:21:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,during some of these classes we\Noccasionally get a no and uh we don't
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.32,1:21:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,even we don't have time to check out the\Nreason for the no at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.88,1:21:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's something you put aside and you\Nsay that's something we'll have to
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.44,1:21:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,investigate later.\NUh so
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.44,1:21:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,because 85% of the population is below\N200 when I wrote power versus force I
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.19,1:21:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,was naive about that. I thought wow\Neverybody can do kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.08,1:21:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I found out later no you can only\Ndo it if you're over 200. Then I looked
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.84,1:21:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,at the calibrated scale of consciousness\Nand I realized that only that means 15%
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.23,1:21:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,of the population can do it.\NOf that 15%
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.56,1:22:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is it 10% that has something wrong with\Ntheir chi energy? Let's ask u right now
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.08,1:22:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,approximately 15% of the population can\Nuse it. Of that 15%
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.28,1:22:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,10% have some problem with their chi\Nenergy. That is correct. You know even
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.19,1:22:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,people who are integris not everybody's\Nadept at it. So it's only one way of
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.80,1:22:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,ascertaining truth. Don't forget\Nkinesiology is really not you know it's
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.48,1:22:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,really a research technique. You don't\Nneed it to reach enlightenment. Buddha
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.88,1:22:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't know kinesiology\Nand all the great saints that ever
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.00,1:22:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,lived. Mother Teresa never heard of it.\NSee and u
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.28,1:22:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,at the time I correspond with Mother\NTeresa Jesus Christ was under attack. I
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.08,1:22:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,think the front cover of time or was\NJesus Christ did he ever really live?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.96,1:22:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Was he a schizophrenic, homosexual, you\Nknow,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.71,1:22:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,all this kind of stuff that periodically\Nsurfaces
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.15,1:23:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and uh so the reality of the divinity of\NJesus Christ was under attack. You know,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.15,1:23:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,those things come up periodically. So I\Njust thought Mother Teresa was would be
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.60,1:23:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,interested in that there's a scientific\Nway of validating the divinity of Christ
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.19,1:23:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,as part of armamentarium of the\Nknowingness of the religious community.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.44,1:23:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway it's really a research tool.\NOccasionally it would be very useful in
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.19,1:23:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,your life but it's not as\Nas as useful as you may think it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.00,1:23:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,because understanding comes out of the\Nadvancement of one's own consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.88,1:23:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We use it uh very often because we're\Nanswering questions from other people or
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.56,1:23:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,because we're investigating new areas.\NYou know, in the writings we do and in
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.88,1:23:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the videotapes and all, you know, we're\Nlooking into things that mankind has
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.96,1:23:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,never had access to, never had access\Nto. It's like, you know, X-rays or the
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.19,1:24:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,electron microscope. uh this whole areas\Nof life that um there was no way of
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.04,1:24:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,investigating\Nand now we have ways of investigating it
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.28,1:24:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course we're always coming up\Nwith questions ourself. So one the
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.15,1:24:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,answer to one question you know lead\Nleads to the next
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.88,1:24:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and there of course is that technique of\Nof self- testing which some people are
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.36,1:24:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,also good at.\NSo that's all I can say about
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.67,1:24:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,kinesiology is it's a thing in itself.
